7c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ R.\">R.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">337c</biblScope></bibl>, etc. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n4496.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> rarely without a question, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀπόγνοια τοῦ ἄλλο τι ἢ κρατεῖν τῆς γῆς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:85\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.85</biblScope></bibl></cit>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}